Plugin(only support flowchart, state and pie)","text":"```mermaid\ninfo\n```\n\n```mermaid\ngraph\nHello --> World\n```\n\n!! 功能特点\n\n* 支持 Mermaid 图表渲染\n* 支持下载 SVG 格式的图表（点击图表左上角的下载按钮）\n* 支持自定义主题和样式\n\n!! 使用方法\n\n使用 ```mermaid 代码块来创建图表：\n\n{{$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/example}}\n\n```mermaid\n---\nconfig:\n  theme: forest\n  look: handDrawn\n---\nflowchart TD\n    Start([2004 TiddlyWiki 发布<br>作者: Jeremy Ruston]) --> Classic[TiddlyWiki Classic]\n\n    Classic -->|插件系统发展| Plugins[插件/宏生态丰富]\n    Classic -->|局限性显现| Limitations[浏览器兼容性差、扩展困难]\n    Classic --> TiddlyWeb[TiddlyWeb 项目尝试]\n\n    Limitations --> Rewrite[重新架构 TW2013]\n    Rewrite --> TW5[TiddlyWiki5 发布2014]\n\n    TW5 --> Features[模块化架构 + 可扩展核心]\n    Features --> NodeSupport[支持 Node.js环境]\n    Features --> ModernUI[现代化界面 + Markdown 支持]\n\n    TW5 -->|持续迭代| Evolve[增强 Tiddler 引擎、插件与主题（2020+）]\n    Evolve --> Future[未来方向：协作、多端同步、更多集成]\n```\n"},"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/codeblock_sub.js":{"title":"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/codeblock_sub.js","text":"/*\\\ntitle: true, browser: true */\n  /*global $tw: false */\n  'use strict';\n\n  exports.baseClass = 'codeblock'; // Extend the <$checkbox> widget\n\n  // Specify a different name to make the subclass available as a new widget instead of overwriting the baseclass:\n  // exports.name = \"my-enhanced-checkbox\";\n\n  exports.constructor = function (parseTreeNode, options) {\n    this.initialise(parseTreeNode, options);\n  };\n\n  exports.prototype = {};\n  exports.prototype.render = function (parent, nextSibling) {\n    this.parentDomNode = parent;\n    this.computeAttributes();\n    this.execute();\n    var codeNode = this.document.createElement('code'),\n      domNode = this.document.createElement('pre');\n    codeNode.appendChild(\n      this.document.createTextNode(this.getAttribute('code')),\n    );\n    domNode.appendChild(codeNode);\n    parent.insertBefore(domNode, nextSibling);\n    this.domNodes.push(domNode);\n    if (this.postRender) {\n      this.postRender();\n    }\n    if (this.mermaidRender) {\n      this.mermaidRender();\n    }\n  };\n})();\n","type":"application/javascript","module-type":"widget-subclass"},"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/createDownloadBtn.js":{"title":"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/createDownloadBtn.js","text":"/*\\\ntitle: svgContent) {\n  const downloadButton = document.createElement('button');\n  const downloadIcon = $tw.wiki.getTiddlerText(\n    '$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/download-icon',\n  );\n  downloadButton.innerHTML = downloadIcon;\n  downloadButton.title = 'Download SVG';\n  downloadButton.className = 'mermaid-download-btn';\n\n  downloadButton.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n $:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/startup.js\ntype: application/javascript\nmodule-type: startup\n\n\\*/\n\nexports.platforms = ['browser'];\nexports.synchronous = true;\n\nexports.startup = function () {\n  const CodeBlockWidget =\n    require('$:/core/modules/widgets/codeblock.js').codeblock;\n  // const zoomMermaid = require('./zoomMermaid.js')();\n  const downloadSvg = require('./downloadSvg.js');\n  const options = require('./mermaidDefaultConfig.js');\n  const createDownloadBtn = require('./createDownloadBtn.js');\n\n  CodeBlockWidget.prototype.mermaidRender = async function () {\n    const language = this.language;\n    if (language !== 'mermaid') return;\n    const mermaid = require('./mermaid.tiny.js');\n    mermaid.initialize(options);\n\n    const domNode = this.domNodes[0];\n    const mermaidText = domNode.textContent;\n\n    try {\n      await mermaid.parse(mermaidText, {\n        suppressErrors: false,\n      });\n\n      const mermaidId = 'mermaid_' + Date.now();\n      const { svg } = await mermaid.render(mermaidId, mermaidText);\n\n      // 将SVG内容添加到DOM\n      domNode.children[0].outerHTML = svg;\n      // domNode.style.backgroundColor = 'transparent';\n      // domNode.style.border = 'none';\n      createDownloadBtn(domNode, svg);\n\n      // 开启放大和缩小, 拖拽\n      // zoomMermaid(domNode);\n    } catch (e) {\n      domNode.children[0].innerHTML = e.message;\n      domNode.children[0].style.color = 'red';\n    }\n  };\n};\n","type":"application/javascript","module-type":"startup"},"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/styles":{"title":"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/styles","tags":"$:/tags/Stylesheet","text":"\\define mermaid-download-button()\n.mermaid-download-btn {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 5px;\n  left: 5px;\n  z-index: 100;\n  padding: 5px;\n  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n  border: 1px solid #ccc;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  opacity: 0.7;\n  transition: all 0.2s ease;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\n.mermaid-download-btn:hover {\n  opacity: 1;\n  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n}\n\n.mermaid-download-btn svg {\n  width: 14px;\n  height: 14px;\n  vertical-align: middle;\n}\n\n/* 确保 mermaid 容器是相对定位 */\npre.mermaid {\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n/* 确保 mermaid SVG 居中显示 */\npre svg[id^=\"mermaid_\"] {\n  display: block;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  max-width: 100%;\n}\n\n/* 暗色主题适配 */\nhtml.dark .mermaid-download-btn {\n  background-color: rgba(50, 50, 50, 0.7);\n  color: #eee;\n  border-color: #555;\n}\n\nhtml.dark .mermaid-download-btn:hover {\n  background-color: rgba(70, 70, 70, 0.9);\n}\n\\end\n\n<<mermaid-download-button>>\n\n\n\n"},"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/zoomMermaid.js":{"title":"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/zoomMermaid.js","text":"/*\\\ntitle: $:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/zoomMermaid.js\ntype: application/javascript\nmodule-type: library\n\nbased: https://github.com/imzbf/md-editor-rt/blob/52f9faa62b5440d8cffa8acd3a6c2b6debd7a01f/packages/MdEditor/utils/dom.ts#L126\n\\*/\n\n/**\n * 缩放、拖拽mermaid模块\n */\nconst zoomMermaid = () => {\n  const addEvent = (container) => {\n    if (!container) {\n      return;\n    }\n    const content = container.firstChild;\n\n    let scale = 1;\n    let posX = 0;\n    let posY = 0;\n    let isDragging = false;\n    let startX, startY;\n    let initialDistance;\n    let initialScale = 1;\n\n    const updateTransform = () => {\n      content.style.transform = `translate(${posX}px, ${posY}px) scale(${scale})`;\n    };\n\n    container.style.cursor = 'grab';\n    container.style.overflow = 'hidden';\n    container.addEventListener('contextmenu', (e) => {\n      e.stopPropagation();\n      e.preventDefault();\n      scale = 1;\n      posX = 0;\n      posY = 0;\n      updateTransform();\n    });\n\n    // 处理拖拽和单指移动\n    container.addEventListener('touchstart', (event) => {\n      container.style.cursor = 'grabbing';\n      if (event.touches.length === 1) {\n        isDragging = true;\n        startX = event.touches[0].clientX - posX;\n        startY = event.touches[0].clientY - posY;\n      } else if (event.touches.length === 2) {\n        initialDistance = Math.hypot(\n          event.touches[0].clientX - event.touches[1].clientX,\n          event.touches[0].clientY - event.touches[1].clientY,\n        );\n        initialScale = scale;\n      }\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('touchmove', (event) => {\n      event.preventDefault();\n      container.style.cursor = 'grabbing';\n\n      if (isDragging && event.touches.length === 1) {\n        posX = event.touches[0].clientX - startX;\n        posY = event.touches[0].clientY - startY;\n        updateTransform();\n      } else if (event.touches.length === 2) {\n        const newDistance = Math.hypot(\n          event.touches[0].clientX - event.touches[1].clientX,\n          event.touches[0].clientY - event.touches[1].clientY,\n        );\n        const scaleChange = newDistance / initialDistance;\n        const previousScale = scale;\n        scale = initialScale * (1 + (scaleChange - 1)); // 调整缩放速度\n\n        // 计算双指中心点\n        const centerX =\n          (event.touches[0].clientX + event.touches[1].clientX) / 2;\n        const centerY =\n          (event.touches[0].clientY + event.touches[1].clientY) / 2;\n\n        // 获取内容区域的边界\n        const rect = content.getBoundingClientRect();\n        // 计算相对位置\n        const relativeX = (centerX - rect.left) / previousScale;\n        const relativeY = (centerY - rect.top) / previousScale;\n\n        // 调整 posX 和 posY 使得缩放发生在双指中心\n        posX -= relativeX * (scale - previousScale);\n        posY -= relativeY * (scale - previousScale);\n\n        updateTransform();\n      }\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('touchend', () => {\n      container.style.cursor = 'grab';\n      isDragging = false;\n    });\n\n    // PC 端缩放功能\n    container.addEventListener('wheel', (event) => {\n      event.preventDefault();\n      const scaleAmount = 0.02; // 缩放速度\n      const previousScale = scale;\n\n      if (event.deltaY < 0) {\n        // 放大\n        scale += scaleAmount;\n      } else {\n        // 缩小\n        scale = Math.max(0.1, scale - scaleAmount);\n      }\n\n      // 计算鼠标相对于内容的位置\n      const rect = content.getBoundingClientRect();\n      const mouseX = event.clientX - rect.left;\n      const mouseY = event.clientY - rect.top;\n\n      // 调整 posX 和 posY，以使缩放中心为鼠标位置\n      posX -= (mouseX / previousScale) * (scale - previousScale);\n      posY -= (mouseY / previousScale) * (scale - previousScale);\n\n      updateTransform();\n    });\n\n    // PC 端拖拽功能\n    container.addEventListener('mousedown', (event) => {\n      isDragging = true;\n      startX = event.clientX - posX;\n      startY = event.clientY - posY;\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('mousemove', (event) => {\n      if (isDragging) {\n        posX = event.clientX - startX;\n        posY = event.clientY - startY;\n        updateTransform();\n      }\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('mouseup', () => {\n      isDragging = false;\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {\n      isDragging = false;\n    });\n  };\n\n  const handler = (containers) => {\n    addEvent(containers);\n    // containers.forEach((mm) => {\n    //   addEvent(mm);\n    // });\n  };\n\n  return handler;\n};\nmodule.exports = zoomMermaid;\n","type":"application/javascript","module-type":"library"}}}
